        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "Add cost summary display style",
        "body": "## Summary\n\nAdds a configurable display style for local Codex/Claude cost summaries so users can choose:\n\n- **Inline only**: show the summary directly in the main menu.\n- **Submenu only**: show detailed history in the Cost submenu.\n- **Both**: show both presentations.\n\n**Both** remains the migration-safe default, preserving the behavior existing users had before this preference was introduced.\n\n## What changed\n\n- Added the persisted `costSummaryDisplayStyle` preference and localized UI copy.\n- Applied the display choice to local-log cost summaries in the main menu.\n- Preserved the existing arbitrary 1–365 day history control and live cost-refresh diagnostics.\n- Kept provider detail cost data visible regardless of the main-menu display choice.\n- Kept provider-native OpenAI API and Mistral billing dashboards independent of the optional local-log cost toggle.\n- Kept the provider-native OpenAI API billing submenu independent of local cost enablement and display style.\n- Normalized unknown stored values to **Both** and avoided changing the display preference as a side effect of enabling cost summaries.\n- Added focused preference, observation, menu-presentation, provider-detail, and OpenAI API compatibility coverage.\n\n## Validation\n\n- `swift test --filter 'OpenAIAPIStatusMenuTests|StatusMenuCostSummaryDisplayStyleTests'`\n- focused Preferences and provider-detail suites\n- `make check`\n\n## Screenshots\n\n### Menu\n\nBefore:\n\n<img width=\"450\" alt=\"Screenshot 2026-06-24 at 09 54 51\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/7ee2f748-257a-4b0f-a67b-59bffb973ce6\" />\n\nAfter — inline:\n\n<img width=\"311\" height=\"300\" alt=\"Screenshot 2026-06-24 at 09 54 16\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/8682ab67-01ef-456e-8801-8fa6c45f22f0\" />\n\nAfter — submenu:\n\n<img width=\"310\" height=\"146\" alt=\"Screenshot 2026-06-24 at 09 54 32\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/d1e8ac14-8f8e-4a3b-a426-467e59d25778\" />\n\n### Cost setting\n\nBefore:\n\n<img width=\"550\" alt=\"Screenshot 2026-06-27 at 13 27 52\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/d83daddc-a77a-49e3-b6d4-52ea4d4dec23\" />\n\nAfter:\n\n<img width=\"550\" alt=\"Screenshot 2026-06-27 at 13 43 34\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/710e8d2b-4443-46ba-abfd-36ddf04289af\" />",
